<item>
            <title>[LU-15065] buffered write performance regression with PQ enabled</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-15065</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;We found&#160;performance drop in a buffered write up to 15%-20% if compare with a baseline without PQ patches.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;In both cases quota was turned on (enabled=&quot;ugp&quot;) and set only one limit - block hard limit 500T. Also there was at least one OST pool without any quota limits.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Note, this performance issue can&apos;t be seen if there is no OST pools in a system.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
